included?<span class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><span =
lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, =
sans-serif;">The structural claim will require a scope -of works which =
is identified in the process list. The contents claim will have a =
