class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">This can =
all be scheduled now that we have asbestos clearance.<span =
class=3D"xapple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>Do you want me to =
schedule this to occur ASAP?</u><o:p></o:p></span></li><li =
class=3D"xmsonormal" style=3D"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: =
Aptos, sans-serif;"><strong><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size: =
11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Assessment-Only =
Focus</span></strong><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size: 11pt; =
font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: As previously expressed, could we =
limit initial tasks to enabling damage assessment (e.g., securing the =
site, debris removal) rather than repairs (e.g., upstairs =
decontamination, curtain cleaning)? This would allow for a thorough =
